  <brief_title>Ventilation Distribution During Spontaneous Breathing in Healthy Newborn Infants</brief_title>
  <official_title>Ventilation Distribution Observed With Electrical Impedance Tomography (EIT) During Spontaneous Breathing in Healthy Newborn Infants</official_title>
